    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>To white students and faculty at Duke, to our current administration, to our unacknowledged history, I ask one final question: is ‘this’ who we want to be?&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>Lily Levin is a Trinity first-year. Her column, “over-caffeinated convictions,” runs on alternate Fridays.</em></p>

